Output docs/assets/ompconf-demo.gif
Require bun
Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 22
Set Width 1180
Set Height 780
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 8
Set TypingSpeed 1ms
Set Framerate 18
Hide
Type "bun src/cli.ts tui --home demo/fixtures/home --cwd demo/fixtures/home/workspace/example-project --state-dir demo/fixtures/home/.ompconf --screen mcp"
Enter
Sleep 900ms
Show
Tab
Sleep 700ms
Type "/plugin"
Sleep 1000ms
Escape
Sleep 500ms
Hide
Type "q"
Sleep 200ms
